<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.1.1">
<l>meccūtu caṅka miṭattāṉnal vēyūti</l>
<l>poyccūtil tōṟṟa poṟaiyuṭai maṉṉarkkāyp</l>
<l>pattūr peṟātaṉṟu pārataṅ kaiceyta</l>
<l>vattūta ṉappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟā</l>
<l rend="indent">ṉammaṉē yappūcci kāṭṭukiṉṟāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He with the conch that blows in praise on [his] left side,</l>
<l>blowing the good bamboo [flute],</l>
<l>that messenger who had a hand in the Bhārata war</l>
<l rend="indent">—when the ten villages were not obtained—</l>
<l>for the sake of the patient kings</l>
<l rend="indent">who were ruined in the deceitful gambling [game],</l>
<l>he is making [the face of] a hobgoblin.</l>
<l>Oh! He is making [the face of] a hobgoblin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
